des:
Listen to daily motivational quotes performed in song by Ant Utama. For your daily dose of motivation sung in a humorous, not so refined way, you can just say "Alexa, Show Me Courage".

You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
